##Academician Duan Zhengcheng died in Wuhan due to illness

The papernews

The function introduction, has the connotation the current politics new media

Deng Yafei, the paper

According to bright  promising, a member of the Chinese Academy of Engineering, a professor at the Huazhong University of Science and Technology, a chief scientist at the National Engineering Research Center for the digitization of manufacturing equipment and an expert on machine building and automation, Duan Zhengcheng, died February 15,2020, in Wuhan.

According to public information, Academician Duan Zhengcheng is an expert in machinery manufacturing and automation (processing technology and equipment) . Han Chinese, Communist Party member, native of Zhenjiang, Jiangsu Province, expert in machine building and automation. In 1957, he graduated from the Department of Mechanical Engineering of Huazhong University of Science and Technology. He has been engaged in the teaching and research of mechanical manufacturing and automation for a long time. He has been working in the front line, closely linked with production, committed to the country's important needs of automation, digital processing technology and equipment applied basic research and engineering technology research and development. He is currently a professor at the Huazhong University of Science and Technology, a doctoral advisor, and a chief scientist at the National Engineering Research Center for the digitization of manufacturing equipment.

Duan Zhengcheng has won 2 National Science Conference Awards in 1978,1 first-class and 3 second-class national science and Technology Progress Awards, 1 first-class provincial and ministerial science and Technology Progress Award, 7 first-class award and 4 second-class award In 2011, he was awarded the outstanding contribution of science and technology of Hubei Province and published more than 200 papers. He has been appraised as the national outstanding teacher, the Hubei Province Labor model, the Hubei Province advanced education worker and the Hubei Province advanced science and technology worker successively. He led the teaching and research team, in 1993 was awarded as the national advanced collective, and received the "May Day" Labor certificate.
He was elected to the Chinese Academy of Engineering in 2009.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Duan Zhengcheng, academician of Chinese Academy of Engineering and professor of Huazhong University of Science and Technology. Huazhong University of Science and Technology

We need to be able to withstand the "pulse" in scientific research

Academician Duan Zhengcheng devoted his whole life to national science and technology.

For more than 60 years, he has persisted in deepening first-line Enterprise Cooperation, based on the discipline of machinery manufacturing and automation, and oriented to the major needs of the country, carrying out interdisciplinary cross-cutting and integration, and carrying out innovative research and engineering development of high-end equipment, has developed many sets (sets) the international, the domestic initiative high-end automation equipment, and has realized the industrialization in Hubei.

In 2009, at the age of 75, Duan Zhengcheng was elected to the Chinese Academy of Engineering. According to Chutian metropolis daily, Duan Zhengcheng was once encouraged to run for academician, but he refused. The old man regards the title of "academician" as extremely weak, in his opinion, solid scientific research is his interest.

"doing scientific research may not produce great results for 10 or 20 years, so never be impetuous or eager for quick success. If you have chosen your goal, you must persist in it for a long time and be indomitable. Only in this way can we achieve great results and make great achievements." Duan Zhengcheng has a particularly profound experience, he said figuratively: "Do Research to bear loneliness, can not come out of a pulse, they will shock. "

Academician Duan Zhengcheng has made outstanding contributions to Hubei's economic development, scientific and technological progress and personnel training.

At the 2011 Hubei Provincial Science and technology awards conference, Duan Zhengcheng, who won the Hubei Provincial Science and Technology Outstanding Contribution Award, said calmly, "I will treat this honor with a sense of humbleness and trepidation, and treat my future work with a sense of dedication. "

"Here are the trees I planted, and the teachers who have influenced my life. "

In 1953, at the age of 19, Duan Zhengcheng became the first college student to enroll in the Huazhong University of Science and Technology. After graduating in 1957, he stayed on as a teacher and stayed on for more than 60 years. He once said, "here are the trees I planted, and the teachers who have influenced my life. ".

According to a previous report by the Wuhan Evening News, during the initial construction phase of Huazhong Institute of Technology in the 1950s, Duan Zhengcheng and his classmates had to take part in infrastructure construction work during holidays, often planting trees in the morning and working as labourers on the construction site in the afternoon, "There are bricks on the east second floor and the East third floor that I have picked out. A large dining hall is divided into a number of blocks with each block being a classroom. "

Recalling the school's founding years, duan Zhengcheng said with emotion, "although life is hard, it sharpens one's will. And it is because of personal participation that he has a special sense of honor and is willing to make his own efforts for the Development and growth of the school. "

The unity and harmonious environment and atmosphere of his Alma Mater have always been his most cherished place, "The Huazhong Institute of Technology in 1953 was a merger of several disciplines from several schools. From the establishment, the school leaders pay great attention to create a united, cooperative atmosphere. Although teachers come from different schools and professions, the mutual care and help that we have deeply affected our students. It is a fertile land for bringing up talents and making undertakings."

According to the official website of the Huazhong University of Science and Technology, Duan Zhengcheng received two National Science Conference Awards in 1978, three national science and Technology Progress Awards, five provincial and ministerial first class awards and four second class awards during his tenure at the Huazhong University of Science and Technology 217 papers published, 78 papers included in the three major indexes, the chief editor of the "opto-mechatronics Manual" , reference to the "Mechanical Engineering Manual" , the preparation of teaching materials 4,19 patents granted patents 5.

When the master is gone, the glory lives on.
